      "updated": 1779191798452,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Claude Code Agent Teams 关键事实\n\n  - 状态：实验性，需 CLAUDE_CODE_EXPERIMENTAL_AGENT_TEAMS=1 启用，v2.1.32+\n  - 架构：Team Lead + N Teammates，每个独立 context，可直接互发消息（mailbox 系统）\n  - 官方推荐规模：3-5 个 teammate，超过收益递减\n  - 官方原话（架构辩论场景）：\"Have them talk to each other to disprove each other's\ntheories, like a scientific debate. The theory that survives is much more likely to be the\nactual root cause.\"\n  - 支持 subagent 定义复用：可把每个对抗角色定义成 subagent，多场景复用",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "gAuFU-YYnDH1C2TCgAl9Z",
      "originalText": "Claude Code Agent Teams 关键事实\n\n  - 状态：实验性，需 CLAUDE_CODE_EXPERIMENTAL_AGENT_TEAMS=1 启用，v2.1.32+\n  - 架构：Team Lead + N Teammates，每个独立 context，可直接互发消息（mailbox 系统）\n  - 官方推荐规模：3-5 个 teammate，超过收益递减\n  - 官方原话（架构辩论场景）：\"Have them talk to each other to disprove each other's theories, like a scientific debate. The theory that survives is much more likely to be the actual root cause.\"\n  - 支持 subagent 定义复用：可把每个对抗角色定义成 subagent，多场景复用",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
